text.tspan: ...if you know us well, then you'll know that we would rather spend money on travel than stuff
for the house, as we already have everything we need.
If you are thinking of getting us a gift, we'd much prefer you help us make our honeymoon a trip
of a lifetime. We're planning a trip to Australia with a couple of stops in Asia on the way. Our
website www.tie-theknot.co.uk has a gift list of activities, air miles and dining out vouchers that
you can buy for us online.
The main thing is that you come along on our special day to celebrate with us. We look forward to
Thank you for your kind invitation
Send to: 27 Grange Valley Green, Ballyclare, BT39 9HD
